Package: RScriptsandStuff
Title: Machine Learning, Quantitative Finance, and NLP Toolkit in R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Emilio", "Arzamendi", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "emilio@scientialibera.com")
Description: Enterprise-grade R package consolidating machine learning
    classifiers (KNN, XGBoost, CNN), quantitative finance tools (portfolio
    optimization, CAPM screening, ARIMA forecasting), and NLP utilities
    (spam detection, sentiment analysis) into reusable, tested functions
    with full input validation and structured error handling.
